OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,FGreat Western Railway train services
OL,7,Fwill be nationalised on December 13th,
OL,8,Fthe Department for Transport has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FIt will be the 11th operator with a
OL,12,FGovernment contract to be taken into
OL,13,Fpublic ownership. South Western
OL,14,FRailway was the first to transfer into
OL,15,Fpublic ownership last year.
OL,17,FThe three remaining operators in
OL,18,Fprivate ownership will be Avanti West
OL,19,FCoast, CrossCountry and East Midlands
OL,20,FRailway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
