OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,FGWR connects South and South West
OL,7,FEngland, and south Wales, with
OL,8,FPaddington in west London.
OL,10,FA DfT spokesperson said: "This is
OL,11,Fanother significant moment for the
OL,12,FGovernment's flagship public ownership
OL,13,Fprogramme and brings a simpler, more
OL,14,Freliable network under Great British
OL,15,FRailways a step closer.
OL,17,F"The Government is delivering on its
OL,18,Fcommitment to bring services back into
OL,19,Fpublic ownership and put passengers,
OL,20,Fnot shareholders, at the heart of our
OL,21,Frailways."
